Can't assign to _ in declaration where usage in Java signature expects an intrinsic.

{code}
    var epSid: Integer = _
    epSid = 1
    Integer.reverse(epSid)
{code}

Error message is...
{code}
error: type mismatch;
found   : Integer
required: Int
Integer.reverse(epSid)
{code}
Works if you change the first line to:
{code}
var epSid = Integer.MIN_VALUE
{code}

2.8.0 Final
